  "detailed_description": "Enter the mechanical wasteland of <strong><i>LOVE 3</i></strong>, a precision platformer that puts you in control of the last surviving hero, fiveEight. Traverse through 25 minimalistic, but challenging levels. Face rigorous obstacles as you search for hope in a world devoid of it. Unearth hidden secrets and dodge certain doom to the vibrant and catchy soundtrack by James Bennett--tailored to each level. Compete with other players on the Speedrun Leaderboards and push your skills to the limit. Will you be the fastest survivor to brave the dangers that await?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/b89cac7437eadc8999d784398b423353.poster.avif?t=1709579892\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/b89cac7437eadc8999d784398b423353.webm?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/b89cac7437eadc8999d784398b423353.mp4?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SET YOUR OWN CHECKPOINTS</h2>Respawn instantly after every loss of life by placing custom checkpoints with the press of a button. Adapt and diversify the challenges: Limit your checkpoints, number of lives, toggle slow motion, or try out different game modes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/46d5c8cd8aad183c018f735f68660d1f.poster.avif?t=1709579892\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/46d5c8cd8aad183c018f735f68660d1f.webm?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/46d5c8cd8aad183c018f735f68660d1f.mp4?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIDDEN COLLECTABLES AND AREAS</h2>Explore every nook and cranny of the apocalyptic, mechanical wasteland. You'll find secret buttons, entrances, and... survivors?? Remember to keep your eyes peeled, as what you'll find will influence the end of the game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/8548db7ff1701095e318bba757760181.poster.avif?t=1709579892\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/8548db7ff1701095e318bba757760181.webm?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/8548db7ff1701095e318bba757760181.mp4?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 OTHER GAMES INCLUDED FOR FREE</h2>Includes every level from LOVE, LOVE 2: kuso, and LOVE Remastered, in addition to the original 42 track soundtrack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/c74ae290d998c1bdf820ab5c9295966f.poster.avif?t=1709579892\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/c74ae290d998c1bdf820ab5c9295966f.webm?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1604300/extras/c74ae290d998c1bdf820ab5c9295966f.mp4?t=1709579892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
